rComments: Quite charming.  I hear he's married though.  Too bad.
Had him for Labor Econ in 2002.  Then went on to grad school in econ... I still consider Darren to be the best econ teacher I had in college. He's easy on the eyes too.
Ratings are for the classes he taught at the University of Michigan while he was a visiting professor at the School of Public Policy.
